livewallpaper (0.4.0-0) precise; urgency=low

  [ RIVIÈRE Aurélien ]
  * Nexus plugin:
    - Add random pulse color option
  * Configurator:
    - Improve image selector
    - Add folder selector
    - Add selector for multiple folders/images
  * Bugfix:
    - indicator does not find local plugins

  [ Koichi Akabe ]
  * Add photoslide plugin

  [ Maximilian Schnarr ]
  * Add circles plugin
  * Add noise plugin
  * Galaxy plugin:
    - Improve performance
    - Use GLSL shader instead of ARB program for custom galaxy light
  * Nexus plugin:
    - Use range selector for pulse length
  * Configurator:
    - New design
    - Add range selector widget
  * Core:
  	- Add simplex noise functions
  	- Add basic OpenGL shader support
  	- Add LwHSL structure
  	- Improve color conversion functions
  	- Add LwRange structure
  	- Add several utility functions
  * Indicator:
    - Search plugins by plugin file not by schema id
  * Improve custom background options
  * Update documentation
  * Enable compiler optimization to improve performance
  * Bugfixes:
    - live wallpaper stops when system time changes (lp: #1120820)
    - configurator gets false minimum or maximum value if the current
      locale uses , instead of . as decimal mark
  * Translate desktop files
  * Translation updates

 -- Maximilian Schnarr <Maximilian.Schnarr@googlemail.com>  Wed, 20 Feb 2013 12:28:07 +0100

